00:37:04,480 --> 00:37:09,200
 Which raises an important question for us.

864
00:37:09,200 --> 00:37:12,820
 Why is this his reaction?

865
00:37:12,820 --> 00:37:15,940
 He was blind.

866
00:37:15,940 --> 00:37:18,500
 What do you think he wanted to see?

867
00:37:18,500 --> 00:37:19,900
 He got it.

868
00:37:19,900 --> 00:37:22,140
 Like he had already gotten the thing he wanted.

869
00:37:22,140 --> 00:37:23,740
 And so he's in the middle of this interrogation

870
00:37:23,740 --> 00:37:25,340
 in the process of this intimidation.

871
00:37:25,340 --> 00:37:27,440
 And he has his sight.

872
00:37:27,440 --> 00:37:30,980
 In the midst of this conflict,

873
00:37:30,980 --> 00:37:33,460
 why doesn't he just plead the fifth?

