 swap teams and leave Jesus behind and join these guys.

879
00:37:45,940 --> 00:37:47,100
 He has his sight.

880
00:37:47,100 --> 00:37:48,380
 He has what he wants.

881
00:37:48,380 --> 00:37:52,500
 Why does he stand in allegiance to Jesus?

