00:37:52,500 --> 00:37:53,740
 Because, and this is big,

883
00:37:53,740 --> 00:37:55,100
 and I don't need you to miss this,

884
00:37:55,100 --> 00:37:56,900
 one touch from Jesus,

885
00:37:56,900 --> 00:38:01,360
 it didn't just change something in this guy's life.

886
00:38:01,360 --> 00:38:06,280
 It changed everything in this guy's life.

887
00:38:06,280 --> 00:38:09,200
 Which is a really confronting thought

888
