00:38:55,320 --> 00:38:58,060
 Listen, these things are not inherently bad.

908
00:38:58,060 --> 00:39:00,020
 In fact, they're morally neutral.

909
00:39:00,020 --> 00:39:08,660
 But if Jesus Christ is not Lord over all of your life,

