00:40:29,420 --> 00:40:34,580
 Jesus is supreme.

941
00:40:34,580 --> 00:40:38,780
 Jesus is king.

942
00:40:38,780 --> 00:40:42,180
 Jesus is Lord.

943
00:40:42,180 --> 00:40:45,220
 And he gets to sit on the throne of your life.

944
00:40:45,220 --> 00:40:47,860
 That's why one touch from God changes everything.

