00:45:06,740 --> 00:45:10,080
 for that is what he has done in descending from heaven above,

1017
00:45:10,080 --> 00:45:12,340
 coming to earth below, meeting us here,

1018
00:45:12,340 --> 00:45:16,020
 fallen, broken, bruised, broken, and busted humanity.

