00:46:31,940 --> 00:46:34,660
 This is the heart of our King.

1040
00:46:34,660 --> 00:46:37,260
 This is the one thing to know.

1041
00:46:37,260 --> 00:46:43,580
 If you're blind, tonight you can see.

1042
00:46:43,580 --> 00:46:48,660
 One touch, it changes everything.

1043
00:46:49,660 --> 00:46:52,900
 How badly do you want for that touch tonight?

